  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the study is to investigate the psychological effects of burn injuries as
      experienced by patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      We are interested in determining how people adjust to burn injuries as a way of facilitating
      optimal recovery. This is done by conducting several questionnaires at the time of the
      discharge in the hospital, and later follow up with the patients up to two years.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
